  "_comment": [
    "Hand-curated events that the upstream organizations don't publish on their own calendars.",
    "Edit this file, commit, and push — GitHub Actions will pick up the change on the next refresh.",
    "",
    "Each entry has:",
    "  summary           required, the event title",
    "  starts_at         required, ISO local datetime: YYYY-MM-DDTHH:MM (no timezone — see `timezone`)",
    "  duration_minutes  optional, used to compute end time",
    "  location          optional",
    "  description       optional",
    "  url               optional",
    "  timezone          optional, defaults to America/New_York",
    "  recurrence        optional — see below",
    "",
    "Recurrence shapes:",
    "  Weekly on specific weekdays:",
    "    {\"freq\": \"weekly\", \"byday\": [\"WE\"], \"count\": 26}",
    "  Weekly on multiple days:",
    "    {\"freq\": \"weekly\", \"byday\": [\"TU\", \"TH\"], \"until\": \"2026-12-31\"}",
    "  Monthly on a specific day-of-month:",
    "    {\"freq\": \"monthly\", \"bymonthday\": 15}",
    "  Monthly on the Nth weekday (1TU = first Tuesday, 2WE = second Wednesday, -1FR = last Friday):",
    "    {\"freq\": \"monthly\", \"byday\": \"1TU\"}",
    "",
    "Stop conditions: `until` (inclusive end date) or `count` (max occurrences). Without either,",
    "the series expands for ~365 days from now."
